FADE IN:

INT. APARTMENT - DAY

Jane sits at the kitchen table, a single index card in front of her.

JANE
(quietly)
One frame at a time.

She slides the card across the table.

INT. APARTMENT - NIGHT

The same table, the same card, but the light is gone.

Jane looks up at the ceiling. She is not alone.

FADE OUT.

THE END.
